agement-ring-in-18k-white-gold-item-195273?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational">French Pavé WG $1,830</a></td><td><strong>$11,065</strong></td><td>Elevated band sparkle, same stone quality</td></tr><tr><td>$13,000–$15,000</td><td>Lab</td><td><a href="https://www.bluenile.com/diamond-details/28885081?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational">3ct IGI D-IF Ideal</a></td><td><a href="https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/bezel-set-emerald-solitaire-engagement-ring-item-304632?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational">Bezel Solitaire WG $4,300</a></td><td><strong>$13,535</strong></td><td>Modern look, full corner protection at 3ct</td></tr><tr><td>$60,000–$70,000</td><td>Natural</td><td><a href="https://www.bluenile.com/diamond-details/15813280?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational">3.09ct GIA F-VS1 Ideal</a></td><td><a href="https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/riviera-pave-diamond-band-engagement-ring-in-18k-white-gold-item-195326?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational">Riviera Pavé WG $1,515</a></td><td><strong>$65,089</strong></td><td>Natural 3ct entry, GIA-certified</td></tr><tr><td>$78,000+</td><td>Natural</td><td><a href="https://www.bluenile.com/diamond-details/27782883?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational">3.07ct GIA D-FL Ideal</a></td><td><a href="https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/riviera-pave-diamond-band-engagement-ring-in-18k-white-gold-item-195326?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational">Riviera Pavé WG $1,515</a></td><td><strong>$79,057</strong></td><td>Collector grade, D-FL, natural provenance</td></tr></tbody></table>

